# Lychee ignore patterns for link checking
# Patterns in this file will be excluded from link checking
# It supports regular expressions. One expression per line.

# Localhost and example URLs
http://localhost
https://localhost
http://127.0.0.1
https://127.0.0.1
http://example.com
https://example.com
https://github.com/org/repo

# Submodule paths that may not exist in non-recursive checkouts
# The org reusable workflow runs link-check without submodules: recursive
# Local link-checker job uses recursive checkout and validates these paths
file://.*cogni-ai-skills/.*

# URLs that fail due to network blocks
# If DNS/firewall is the issue, allowlist the host in .github/agents/FIREWALL.md
# Only ignore here when link checks still fail after that.
